\{ row( "\($flow2[0]->[2]->[0]\)", "\($flow2[0]->[2]->[1]\)",
	"\($flow2[0]->[2]->[2]\)" ) \}
\{ endtable() \}
$BR
The vector \($flow2[0]->[1]->[1]\) is at the point
\{ ans_rule(35) \}
$BR
${BITALIC}(Give an (x,y) ordered pair.)$EITALIC

END_TEXT
